{"tid":1681231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有6名原被控「非法集結」罪的被告遭改控「暴動」罪。","createTime":"2019-10-29T09:40:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T11:35:47.000Z","uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2285b2d0519e925d3be11c702f7a2a7386c22dd3","tid":1681231,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:40:14.000Z","msg":"0930 #被捕人士 #沙田 #新城市廣場 #機場<br />\n<br />\n昨日下午東區裁判法院有9人再提堂，分別涉及7月14日沙田大遊行、8月13日機場襲擊警員致拔槍事件，以及禁錮《環時》記者付國豪事件。法庭應控方申請，將9人合併成3宗案件，並轉介至區域法院審理，將於下月進行答辯。其中有6名原被控「非法集結」罪的被告遭改控「暴動」罪。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nAm7AHK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnAm7AHK.jpg&h=a58a061c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報導全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1068225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1068225&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2BsgxjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=7825025f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1068225&h=11806587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1068225</a><br />\n#獨媒"},{"pid":"57fe13ba8c949cb7d61c90f6fa508b7eca75e165","tid":1681231,"uid":136893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:41:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記唔記得7、8月既時候，臨有行動前一日既連登，係充滿住遊行路線、離開方法、行動目的地既街坊整既攻略、仲有各種各樣既行動資訊整合，所有行動都係至小早半個月搞，有D 活動更加係會根據其重要性去調配，例如我記得葵青區遊行係推遲左成個月的。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n反思行動及行動數量<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（極緊急！！！）等我教大家點再引發群眾熱情<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680895</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"748780c4a3f7027b9c3dbfac3157babb40f17b7b","tid":1681231,"uid":252292,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:42:57.000Z","msg":"因為非法集結都告唔入，所以是9旦改條重罪嚇9人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72959b8b3d685b712a15c864c7617b4ec850ab7c","tid":1681231,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"748780c4a3f7027b9c3dbfac3157babb40f17b7b","tid":1681231,"uid":252292,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:42:57.000Z","msg":"因為非法集結都告唔入，所以是9旦改條重罪嚇9人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:43:44.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5411c93413dc6a9be68b75c56908545ed972514c","tid":1681231,"uid":9116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"748780c4a3f7027b9c3dbfac3157babb40f17b7b","tid":1681231,"uid":252292,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:42:57.000Z","msg":"因為非法集結都告唔入，所以是9旦改條重罪嚇9人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:45:06.000Z","msg":"唔係咁講呀，而家係加重條罪，即係啲狗都有掌握一定證據"},{"pid":"7c61ca1f5e737582e3bb98bd0cab7ead3b29d3d9","tid":1681231,"uid":214635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:46:25.000Z","msg":"告暴動係咪就要陪審團？唔識"},{"pid":"6b8274fc935dc90b3f4d38a8927dcb4b7f4e0786","tid":1681231,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:52:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"058b65e57c2b27764c999f597fce95c49f56b23a","tid":1681231,"uid":180168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c61ca1f5e737582e3bb98bd0cab7ead3b29d3d9","tid":1681231,"uid":214635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:46:25.000Z","msg":"告暴動係咪就要陪審團？唔識"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:54:50.000Z","msg":"區域法院無陪審團"},{"pid":"07c15978ab81f457ddea77597089468f65a7e91d","tid":1681231,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:57:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>主線速遞</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets